727798f-a.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - 67th Drive
727798f-a.text:
Queens Boulevard, south side, east of 67th Dr. (formerly Pilogrim Street), showing the shewing of the embankment on the Boulevwrd and the completion of the widening ef it for this area
of Queens County.
March 1925.
Views 1 and 2
View 3: May 1926.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
